WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
Start on the exact operational screen for this guide.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
Check-Ins turns the schedule into the daily operations board.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.500
Read lane counts before opening individual rentals.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Blocked pickups go to Overview to clear payment, agreement, counter-sign, insurance, or readiness.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.500
Pickup cards open Check-In; return and settlement cards open Check-Out.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.000
Open the exact rental before recording return, override, charges, or deposit settlement.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.500
Do not hand over or close out a vehicle if inspection, license, payment, or damage status is unresolved.

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:20.000
Use Check-Ins to clear pickup and return blockers for today.
